{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"35296-kaiaem-thub","title":"ແມ່ໄກ່ຄາວຽກ","description":"ແມ່ໄກ່ນັ່ງຟັກໄຂ່ດ້ວຍຄວາມອົດທົນລໍໃຫ້ໄຂ່ຂອງມັນເບາະອອກມາ. ອີກດົນປານໄກ່ນ້ອຍຈິ່ງຈະເບາະອອກມາ? ພາກັນຊ່ວຍແມ່ໄກ່ນັບໄກ່ນ້ອຍໄດ້ບໍ່?","language":"Lao","langCode":"lo","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Phuangthana  Phetsavong"],"illustrators":["Aphisith Souphavongtay"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/35296-kaiaem-thub"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93901/size3/28d55955f272bfc6991e98ebea109562.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93901/size6/28d55955f272bfc6991e98ebea109562.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69625/size6/d8ca1a9559cbde66aa8af0a7d7ebfc1f.jpg","text":"ໄກ່ແມ່ໂຕໜຶ່ງນັ່ງຟັກໄຂ່ຂອງມັນດ້ວຍຄວາມອົດທົນ\nເພື່ອລໍໃຫ້ລູກໄກ່ ເບາະອອກມາ","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69627/size6/dc4ab697d52dca2816b14b4c4f73472f.jpg","text":"ແມ່ແບ້ຍ່າງຜ່ານມາ “ເຈົ້າບໍ່ໄປຕະຫຼາດນັດຫວາແມ່ໄກ່ເອີ້ຍ?”\n\"ກະຕ໋າກ! ກະຕ໋າກ! ຂ້ອຍຄາຟັກໄຂ່ຂອງຂ້ອຍຢູ່”.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69629/size6/3c9a6b4480d3970772b430b573204a30.jpg","text":"ໜຶ່ງ, ສອງ, ສາມ ສີ່, ຫ້າ, ຫົກ,","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69630/size6/b638c7096e297ee3d2cc408aa7849206.jpg","text":"ໄຂ່ກົມໆຫົກໜ່ວຍ.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71829/size6/ad7b69b8f67b9569fc53fdac229d7fbf.jpg","text":"ແມ່ໝູຍ່າງມາຫາ\n“ເຈົ້າບໍ່ໄປຕະຫຼາດນັດຫວາແມ່ໄກ່ເອີ້ຍ?”","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71830/size6/cc99ccb16d0d8334ac244825aa10d439.jpg","text":"\"ກະຕ໋າກ! ກະຕ໋າກ! ຂ້ອຍຄາຟັກໄຂ່ຂອງຂ້ອຍຢູ່”.ໜຶ່ງ, ສອງ, ສາມ ສີ່, ຫ້າ, ຫົກ, ໄຂ່ຂາວໆຫົກໜ່ວຍ","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69633/size6/2be9f232b8a89c9df6b2622f86d2e693.jpg","text":"ແມ່ງົວຍ່າງຜ່ານມາ\n“ເຈົ້າບໍ່ໄປຕະຫຼາດນັດຫວາແມ່ໄກ່ເອີ້ຍ?”","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69634/size6/549067838b365fb9e46f1461b3241700.jpg","text":"\"ກະຕ໋າກ! ກະຕ໋າກ! ຂ້ອຍຄາຟັກໄຂ່ຂອງຂ້ອຍຢູ່”.\nໜຶ່ງ, ສອງ, ສາມ, ສີ່, ຫ້າ, ຫົກ, ໄຂ່ມົນໆຫົກໜ່ວຍ.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69644/size6/ef424b085fb4a953bd6fd01d883ac978.jpg","text":"10/18","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69636/size6/b2b299a9d79df34e8080765c7c7bac88.jpg","text":"ແມ່ໄກ່ຄອງຄອຍດ້ວຍຄວາມອົດທົນ “ເມື່ອໃດລູກຈຶ່ງຈະເບາະອອກມານໍ້”","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69637/size6/89228c4c149286f8a769352401052cda.jpg","text":"ແມ່ໄກ່ນັ່ງຟັກໄຂ່ຕໍ່ໄປ.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69638/size6/737b566c58604ab24d9e524d3eb8ca2b.jpg","text":"ໜຶ່ງ, ສອງ, ສາມ, ສີ່, ຫ້າ, ຫົກ, “ປ໋ອກ! ປ໋ອກ!” ທັນໃດໄກ່ນ້ອຍຫົກໂຕທີ່ໜ້າຮັກ ກໍເບາະອອກມາ","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69639/size6/16d14045c4552e7cbafe3f7360641149.jpg","text":"14/18","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/71835/size6/2345d7a8da786624885456a4305a6c40.jpg","text":"ແມ່ໄກ່ນຶກໄດ້ວ່າມີງານຕະຫຼາດນັດ\nມັນຟ້າວພາລູກທັງຫົກລົງຈາກຮັງ ແລ້ວໄປງານຕະຫຼາດນັດ","words":null},{"n":15,"img"